      "seed": 234511825,
      "version": 449,
      "versionNonce": 317563761,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767769872939,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The board u r building is from an ecosystem it's\nnot the only thing in the world u have to keep in\nmind everything else, it might talk to peripherals\nWI-FI BLE, u must keep the ecosystem in mind if\nu don't do that u will fail.",
      "rawText": "The board u r building is from an ecosystem it's not the only thing in the world u have to keep in mind everything else, it might talk to peripherals WI-FI BLE, u must keep the ecosystem in mind if u don't do that u will fail.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The board u r building is from an ecosystem it's not the only thing in the world u have to keep in mind everything else, it might talk to peripherals WI-FI BLE, u must keep the ecosystem in mind if u don't do that u will fail.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Itz5kT1E",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -500,
      "y": 320,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 140,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1329377695,
      "version": 822,
      "versionNonce": 2000245951,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767769875722,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When we talk on the board level (the PCB) u just\ncan't thing about one sensor and forget\neverything else u must think about how everything\nwork with each other, u might give all the\nrecourses to one component and the others will\njust tell u please just give me a little time to\nprocess.",
      "rawText": "When we talk on the board level (the PCB) u just can't thing about one sensor and forget everything else u must think about how everything work with each other, u might give all the recourses to one component and the others will just tell u please just give me a little time to process.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When we talk on the board level (the PCB) u just can't thing about one sensor and forget everything else u must think about how everything work with each other, u might give all the recourses to one component and the others will just tell u please just give me a little time to process.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
